Ing '''lawi'''  mipakaba yang panaun nung kapilan lalto ing kakulangan ning metung a labuad king danum a makukua karin, king babo man o king lalam gabun. Malyari yang lumuat ing lawing pilang bulan o banwa, o malyari yang mideklara o mibulalag kilub na mu ning labing limang (15) aldo.<ref>[http://www.independent.ie/irish-news/its-a-scorcher-and-ireland-is-officially-in-drought-29431138.html It's a scorcher - and Ireland is officially 'in drought'] Irish Independent, 2013-07-18.</ref> Keraklan, malilyari iti nung taglus-taglus yang mas mababa kesa king karaniwan o ''average'' ing mababaldug a uran o [[precipitation (meteorology)|precipitation]] . Malyari yang mika maragul a epektu king [[ecosystem]] ampo king [[agrikultura]] ning miyapektuang lugal. Lipat ning malyari lang lumbat pilang banwa deng lawi, malyari yang magdalang makabaldugang kasiran ing anggiang makuyad oneng mabayat a lawi <ref>[http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/drought/livedrought.shtml Living With Drought<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> and harm to the local [[economy]].<ref>[http://www.lilith-ezine.com/articles/environmental/Australian-Drought.html Australian Drought and Climate Change], retrieved on June 7th 2007.</ref> 

